U.K. Protest Group Hacks Into Vodafone Website, Guardian Reports

-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 
2011-03-11T00:30:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-11/u-k-protest-group-hacks-into-vodafone-website-guardian-reports.html
A protest group opposing government
spending cuts and corporate tax avoidance hacked into the
website of  Vodafone Group Plc (VOD)  and posted blogs criticizing the
company, the Guardian reported.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Simpson at 
 jsimpson12@bloomberg.net  